'''2021年综合拨款法'''（{{USBill|116|HR|133}}），是一项2.3万亿美元<ref name="The Hill Congress unveils $2.3 trillion">{{cite web |last1=Elis |first1=Niv |title=Congress unveils $2.3 trillion government spending and virus relief package |url=https://thehill.com/policy/finance/531164-congress-unveils-23-trillion-government-spending-and-virus-relief-package |website=The Hill |access-date=21 December 2020 |archive-date=2021-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323184407/https://thehill.com/policy/finance/531164-congress-unveils-23-trillion-government-spending-and-virus-relief-package |dead-url=no }}</ref>的支出[[撥款法案_(美國)|撥款法案]]，该法案将9000亿美元用于缓解美国的冠状病毒大流行，以及1.4万亿美元用于2021联邦财政年度的综合支出法案（合并12项单独的年度拨款法案），并防止[[美國政府停擺|政府关门]]。<ref name="PoliticoRoundup">Caitlin Emma & Marianne LeVine, [https://www.politico.com/news/2020/12/20/details-stimulus-package-omnibus-bill-449499 Breaking down the $900B stimulus package and $1.4T omnibus bill] {{Wayback|url=https://www.politico.com/news/2020/12/20/details-stimulus-package-omnibus-bill-449499 |date=20210302150810 }}, ''Politico'' (December 20, 2020).</ref><ref name="Bloomberg Congress update">{{cite web |title=Virus Relief Bill Released Hours Before Vote: Congress Update |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-12-21/relief-bill-set-for-votes-in-house-senate-congress-update |website=Bloomberg |access-date=21 December 2020 |archive-date=2021-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210219165202/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-12-21/relief-bill-set-for-votes-in-house-senate-congress-update |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="BI delayed text">{{cite web |last1=Lahut |first1=Jake |title='A bad time to have a computer glitch': COVID-19 stimulus bill text delayed by printer errors and internet issues |url=https://www.businessinsider.com/stimulus-bill-text-delayed-by-printer-errors-and-internet-issues-2020-12 |website=Business Insider |access-date=21 December 2020 |archive-date=2021-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210101012802/https://www.businessinsider.com/stimulus-bill-text-delayed-by-printer-errors-and-internet-issues-2020-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>该法案是有史以来颁布的规模最大的支出法案之一，超过了2020年3月颁布的2.2万亿美元的{{link-en|关怀法案|CARES Act}}。<ref name="The Hill Congress unveils $2.3 trillion" />这项法案是自2020年4月以来第一个针对冠状病毒大流行的法案。<ref name="lat-passed">{{cite news|date=December 21, 2020|title=Congress approves new stimulus plan that includes checks for many Americans|newspaper=Los Angeles Times|url=https://www.latimes.com/politics/story/2020-12-21/congress-includes-historic-measures-in-government-funding-pandemic-relief-bills|author-first=Jennifer|author-last=Haberkorn|accessdate=2021-02-15|archive-date=2021-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210219173137/https://www.latimes.com/politics/story/2020-12-21/congress-includes-historic-measures-in-government-funding-pandemic-relief-bills|dead-url=no}}</ref>据参议院历史办公室的数据，该法案长达5593页，是国会有史以来通过的最长法案。

该法案于2020年12月21日获得国会参众两院通过，得到了两党多数议员的支持。这项法案是民主党和共和党在{{link-en|跛脚鸭会期|Lame-duck session}}期间数周紧张谈判和妥协的产物。<ref>Grace Segers, [https://www.cbsnews.com/news/covid-relief-bill-unemployment-stimulus-900-billion/ What's in the $900 billion coronavirus relief bill passed by Congress?] {{Wayback|url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/covid-relief-bill-unemployment-stimulus-900-billion/ |date=20210331021552 }}, CBS News (December 23, 2020).</ref><ref name="CNN House approves">{{cite web |last1=Foran |first1=Clare |last2=Raju |first2=Manu |title=House approves $900 billion Covid rescue package, sending it to the Senate |url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/12/21/politics/stimulus-deal-votes/index.html |website=CNN |access-date=22 December 2020 |archive-date=2021-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210326122015/https://www.cnn.com/2020/12/21/politics/stimulus-deal-votes/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last1=Stein|first1=Jeff|last2=DeBonis|first2=Mike|title=Senate approves huge spending package, sends economic relief measure to Trump for enactment|language=en-US|work=Washington Post|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/us-policy/2020/12/21/stimulus-congress/|access-date=2020-12-22|issn=0190-8286|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121232251/https://www.washingtonpost.com/us-policy/2020/12/21/stimulus-congress/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://thehill.com/homenews/senate/531223-congress-passes-23t-coronavirus-relief-government-funding-deal |title=Congress passes $2.3T coronavirus relief, government funding deal |author=Carney, Jordain |website=The Hill |access-date=December 22, 2020 |archive-date=2021-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129115311/https://thehill.com/homenews/senate/531223-congress-passes-23t-coronavirus-relief-government-funding-deal |dead-url=no }}</ref>在最初批评该法案后，唐纳德·特朗普总统于12月27日将其签署成为法律。<ref name="CNBC Trump signs">{{cite web |last1=Pramuk |first1=Jacob |title=Trump signs Covid relief and government funding bill days after he suggested he would block it |url=https://www.cnbc.com/2020/12/28/trump-signs-covid-relief-and-government-funding-bill-days-after-suggesting-hed-block-it.html |website=CNBC.com |access-date=28 December 2020 |archive-date=2021-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320151233/https://www.cnbc.com/2020/12/28/trump-signs-covid-relief-and-government-funding-bill-days-after-suggesting-hed-block-it.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="nyt-1222">{{cite news|last1=Broadwater|first1=Luke|last2=Rappeport|first2=Alan|date=December 22, 2020|title=Trump Demands Changes to Coronavirus Relief Bill, Calling It a 'Disgrace'|newspaper=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/22/us/politics/trump-coronavirus-bill.html|access-date=2020-12-24|archive-date=2021-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210327032213/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/22/us/politics/trump-coronavirus-bill.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="USA Today Trump signs">{{cite web|last1=Fritze|first1=John|last2=Subramanian|first2=Courtney|title=Trump reverses on coronavirus stimulus deal, signs package he called a 'disgrace'|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2020/12/27/trump-signs-900-b-covid-relief-package-he-called-disgrace/4023316001/|access-date=28 December 2020|website=USA Today|archive-date=2021-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210218000517/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2020/12/27/trump-signs-900-b-covid-relief-package-he-called-disgrace/4023316001/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

